> A.  Has anyone got any wisdom for replacing them with Webers (either twin 
> 40 or progressive)?
> 
> B.  Anyone got any wisdom on making them work better?  Idle is poor, hot 
> starting poor, not very economical and not smooth around town - but OK 
> cruising on a motorway.
> 
> I am in London - any local experts who could set them up or supply a 
> service kit?
